      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节零食商城</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        color: #333333;\n    }\n    header {\n        background-color: #D0021B;\n        padding: 10px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    header input {\n        width: 80%;\n        padding: 8px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    nav {\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        padding: 10px;\n    }\n    nav ul {\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n        list-style: none;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-around;\n    }\n    nav ul li {\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    section {\n        padding: 20px;\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #product-gallery div {\n        height: 200px;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    #product-gallery p {\n        text-align: center;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        color: #D0021B;\n    }\n    #product-specs h2 {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #product-specs ul {\n        list-style: disc inside;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n    #pricing-promo p {\n        margin: 5px 0;\n    }\n    #pricing-promo div {\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        padding: 10px;\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #pricing-promo button {\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        background-color: #D0021B;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #purchase-options h3 {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #purchase-options div {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #purchase-options div button {\n        padding: 8px 12px;\n        border: 1px solid #D0021B;\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #purchase-options p {\n        color: #333333;\n        font-size: 14px;\n    }\n    #comment-section h3 {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #comment-section div {\n        min-height: 100px;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        padding: 10px;\n    }\n    #comment-section select {\n        padding: 8px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    }\n    footer {\n        position: fixed;\n        bottom: 0;\n        width: 100%;\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;\n        padding: 10px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    footer div {\n        flex: 1;\n    }\n    footer p {\n        flex: 0 0 auto;\n        margin: 0 10px;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        color: #D0021B;\n    }\n    footer button {\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        background-color: #D0021B;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<header id=\"search-bar\">\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"站内搜索：输入关键字查找春节零食商品\">\n</header>\n\n<nav id=\"nav-bar\">\n    <ul>\n        <li>主页</li>\n        <li>分类</li>\n        <li>购物车</li>\n    </ul>\n</nav>\n\n<section id=\"product-gallery\">\n    <div>轮播图片容器</div>\n    <p>春节主题零食，助你佳节团圆</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"product-specs\">\n    <h2>规格说明</h2>\n    <ul>\n        <li>精美礼盒包装</li>\n        <li>多口味组合</li>\n        <li>独立小包装</li>\n    </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"pricing-promo\">\n    <p>原价：￥99</p>\n    <p>现价：￥79</p>\n    <div>促销剩余时间：00天 12:34:56</div>\n    <button>领取优惠券</button>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"purchase-options\">\n    <h3>选择购买规格</h3>\n    <div>\n        <button>10包</button>\n        <button>20包</button>\n        <button>30包</button>\n    </div>\n    <p>购买更多享受更大优惠</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"comment-section\">\n    <h3>用户评论</h3>\n    <div>评论列表容器</div>\n    <select>\n        <option>全部评论</option>\n        <option>好评</option>\n        <option>中评</option>\n        <option>差评</option>\n    </select>\n</section>\n\n<footer id=\"buy-now-modal\">\n    <div>已选商品：20包礼盒装</div>\n    <p>最终价格：￥79</p>\n    <button>立即支付</button>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
